{"id":4676,"date":"2019-10-02T17:19:39","date_gmt":"2019-10-02T17:19:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=4676"},"modified":"2020-02-14T23:29:22","modified_gmt":"2020-02-14T16:29:22","slug":"9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/","title":{"rendered":"9 Xu H\u01b0\u1edbng Thi\u1ebft K\u1ebf Th\u01b0\u01a1ng Hi\u1ec7u M\u1edbi Nh\u1ea5t 2020"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Logo_bien_doi\" title=\"Logo bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i\">Logo bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#i\" title=\"\u00a0\">\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Font_chu_bat_mat\" title=\"Font ch\u1eef b\u1eaft m\u1eaft\u00a0\">Font ch\u1eef b\u1eaft m\u1eaft\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Thiet_ke_hinh_hoc_than_thien_hon\" title=\"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Logo_va_bao_bi_lay_cam_hung_tu_su_co_dien\" title=\"Logo v\u00e0 bao b\u00ec l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n\">Logo v\u00e0 bao b\u00ec l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Chi_tiet_phuc_tap\" title=\"Chi ti\u1ebft ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p\u00a0\">Chi ti\u1ebft ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Nghe_thuat_diem_anh\" title=\"Ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea3nh\u00a0\">Ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea3nh\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Ma_mi\" title=\"Ma m\u1ecb\u00a0\">Ma m\u1ecb\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Hinh_anh_3D\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3D\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3D<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/9-xu-huong-thiet-ke-thuong-hieu-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Khong_gian_am\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng gian \u00e2m\">Kh\u00f4ng gian \u00e2m<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\r\n<p><em>Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho n\u0103m 2019 chuy\u1ec3n sang hai con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 ho\u00e0i c\u1ed5, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u0103m 2019, tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u ch\u00fang l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u00fang \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. V\u00ec v\u1eady, sau khi ph\u00e2n t\u00edch <strong>xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/strong> cho logo, bao b\u00ec s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf web, ki\u1ec3u ch\u1eef v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda n\u00f3i chung, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch 10<strong> xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t<\/strong> cho n\u0103m 2019.<\/em><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Logo_bien_doi\"><\/span><strong>Logo bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u00e3y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi<strong> xu h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2019<\/strong> b\u1edfi n\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c marketer thay th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng logo l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng logo bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n logo kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho t\u1eebng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng. Logo cho \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng di \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. In qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t th\u00ec h\u00e3y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng logo \u0111en tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed. Ch\u1ea1y m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ebb em th\u00ec l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>H\u00e3y ghi nh\u1edb 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh sau \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh logo:<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsive<\/strong>: \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch tr\u00ean c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng k\u0129 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1, logo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n n\u00ean thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ( m\u00e1y t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i\u2026)<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Contextual<\/strong>: b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh,logo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 n\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ( v\u00ed d\u1ee5: logo m\u1ed9t t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u in n\u1ed5i tr\u00ean danh thi\u1ebfp, logo t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u0169 b\u00f3ng ch\u00e0y )<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Variable<\/strong>: s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh trong logo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t chung<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4677\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/attachment_63424222-e1546526555918-669x1024.png\" alt=\"thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\" width=\"851\" height=\"1303\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/attachment_63424222-e1546526555918-669x1024.png 669w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/attachment_63424222-e1546526555918-196x300.png 196w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/attachment_63424222-e1546526555918-768x1176.png 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/attachment_63424222-e1546526555918.png 930w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"i\"><\/span>\u00a0<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Font_chu_bat_mat\"><\/span><strong>Font ch\u1eef b\u1eaft m\u1eaft\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, <strong>ch\u1ee7 ngh\u0129a t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n<\/strong> \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u00ec t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a n\u00f3: <em>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n nhanh h\u01a1n,dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n tr\u00ean m\u00e0n \u1ea3nh nh\u1ecf<\/em>. Nh\u01b0ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng serif g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Serif<\/strong>: Nh\u1eefng nh\u00e3n nh\u1ecf \u1edf cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00e0o l\u01b0u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1edbn trong xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n nh\u1eefng n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00fang \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2019 b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.N\u0103m nay, serifs r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho xu h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4678\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/font-chu-co-chan-thiet-ke-website-1.jpg\" alt=\"xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u\" width=\"851\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/font-chu-co-chan-thiet-ke-website-1.jpg 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/font-chu-co-chan-thiet-ke-website-1-300x160.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Serif ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1t trong c\u00e1c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1, logo nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho c\u00e1c kh\u1ed1i v\u0103n b\u1ea3n l\u1edbn. Serifs c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c slogan c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean blog ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3n sao trang web c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00f4ng r\u1ed1i m\u1eaft.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thiet_ke_hinh_hoc_than_thien_hon\"><\/span><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong vi\u1ec7c <strong>x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/strong> l\u00e0 <strong>h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc.<\/strong> Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u b\u1eb1ng h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng, c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i tr\u1eebu t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u01b0\u1edbi. Phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac v\u00e0 tr\u1eadt t\u1ef1, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 ngh\u0129a hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch t\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0: nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf to\u00e1n h\u1ecdc n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi g\u00e2y ra s\u1ef1 ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t. V\u1eady th\u00ec, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4679\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-ke-logo-sao-kim-8.jpg\" alt=\"x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u\" width=\"851\" height=\"569\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-ke-logo-sao-kim-8.jpg 600w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-ke-logo-sao-kim-8-300x201.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i k\u0129 thu\u1eadt l\u00e0m cho h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn h\u01a1n trong n\u0103m 2019 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u00fang v\u1edbi m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u1ea5m \u00e1p, s\u1ef1 vui t\u01b0\u01a1i l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 u \u00e1m v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch. Th\u1ee9 hai, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong, h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 vui t\u01b0\u01a1i h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 g\u00f3c nh\u1ecdn.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Logo_va_bao_bi_lay_cam_hung_tu_su_co_dien\"><\/span><strong>Logo v\u00e0 bao b\u00ec l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t cu h\u01b0\u1edbng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, trong n\u0103m 2019, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i sinh c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng qua thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo v\u00e0 bao b\u00ec<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4680\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/logo-2016-16.jpg\" alt=\"xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u\" width=\"851\" height=\"566\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/logo-2016-16.jpg 600w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/logo-2016-16-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00e1c logo l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eadp trung xung quanh m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u00ednh, th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh minh h\u1ecda v\u1ebd tay, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t trong m\u1ed9t khung bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng bao g\u1ed3m t\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00f4ng ch\u1eef vi\u1ebft tay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00e0 kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u n\u1ebfu c\u00f3. c\u00e1c logo c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n bao g\u1ed3m \u00a0n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp. Ch\u00fang c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u l\u00e0m cho logo b\u1ecb phong h\u00f3a, khu\u1ebfch \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00e2n th\u1ef1c.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Bao b\u00ec c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o b\u1eb1ng tay v\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u ch\u1eef c\u0169, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 s\u1ebd vi\u1ebft t\u00ean c\u00f4ng ty d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng s\u00f3ng ho\u1eb7c nghi\u00eang.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chi_tiet_phuc_tap\"><\/span><strong>Chi ti\u1ebft ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Serif kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i xu h\u01b0\u1edbng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 ngh\u0129a t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n. m\u1ed9t xu h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed v\u00e0 hoa \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 t\u00ednh h\u01a1n.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4681\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/e6c59d53-86dd-48fe-8d3d-29f682ed9cc4-e1546525096915.jpg\" alt=\"xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo 2020\" width=\"851\" height=\"591\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/e6c59d53-86dd-48fe-8d3d-29f682ed9cc4-e1546525096915.jpg 930w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/e6c59d53-86dd-48fe-8d3d-29f682ed9cc4-e1546525096915-300x208.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/e6c59d53-86dd-48fe-8d3d-29f682ed9cc4-e1546525096915-768x533.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>L\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb phong c\u00e1ch trang tr\u00ed baroque v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh minh h\u1ecda v\u1ebd tay, xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt b\u1edfi c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf. m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u2013 T\u00f4 b\u00f3ng<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u2013 Trang tr\u00ed c\u00f4ng phu<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u2013 L\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o nhau<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u2013 Nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft tinh t\u1ebf (l\u00f4ng mi,n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, l\u00f4ng ch\u00e2n tay\u2026)<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u2013 \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00e2m v\u00e0 song song<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u2013 H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nghe_thuat_diem_anh\"><\/span><strong>Ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea3nh\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0o th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ? H\u00e3y th\u1eed Pixel Art, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c video game nh\u1eefng th\u1eadp ni\u00ean 80 v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch k\u0129 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4682\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/pixel-logo-design.jpg\" alt=\"m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\" width=\"851\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/pixel-logo-design.jpg 660w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/pixel-logo-design-300x99.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Pixel art, hay ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt 8-bit, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh vu\u00f4ng l\u1edbn, \u0111\u01a1n s\u1eafc, gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp ch\u00fang th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft. \u00a0b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh hay linh v\u1eadt gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eeb m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 80 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ma_mi\"><\/span><strong>Ma m\u1ecb\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Trong khi c\u00e1c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng typography d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 tu\u00e2n theo nh\u1eefng quy t\u1eafc ri\u00eang th\u00ec l\u1ea1i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n xu h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u00e1c ch\u1eef c\u00e1i ma m\u1ecb ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u1eef c\u00e1i trong su\u1ed1t cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh anh h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1eadp ni\u00ean 2010. C\u00e1c n\u00fat m\u1edd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh anh h\u00f9ng v\u00ec ch\u00fang che khu\u1ea5t \u00edt h\u01a1n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef l\u1edbn t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u00fang \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3u ch\u1eef ma m\u1ecb, ki\u1ec3u ch\u1eef to v\u00e0 c\u1ed3ng k\u1ec1nh v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u1ec1n.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hinh_anh_3D\"><\/span>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3D<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng to l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn xu h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. Khi m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1edbi, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i n\u00e2ng cao ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u mong \u0111\u1ee3i m\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4683\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/79113715f49bce05540697ac2346e730.jpg\" alt=\"xu huong thuong hieu\" width=\"851\" height=\"542\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/79113715f49bce05540697ac2346e730.jpg 680w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/79113715f49bce05540697ac2346e730-300x191.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta th\u1ea5y x\u1ea3y ra g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3D. m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3D \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, l\u00e0m m\u1edd ranh gi\u1edbi gi\u1eefa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh do m\u00e1y t\u00ednh t\u1ea1o ra. Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t \u00a0cho logo, h\u00ecnh n\u1ec1n v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 ch\u1eef; Khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng th\u1ea5y m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng minh c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Khong_gian_am\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u00f4ng gian \u00e2m<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c<strong> xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/strong> \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t s\u1edf th\u00edch \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t xu h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian \u00e2m t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong logo c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00f4ng minh.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4684\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/attachment_97721300-e1542202780605.jpeg\" alt=\"logo th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u\" width=\"851\" height=\"517\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/attachment_97721300-e1542202780605.jpeg 930w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/attachment_97721300-e1542202780605-300x182.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/attachment_97721300-e1542202780605-768x467.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng gian \u00e2m \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ed9t \u1ea5n \u00fd hay th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a n\u00f3 l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. N\u00f3 cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 2 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh trong m\u1ed9t. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian \u00e2m thanh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m cho logo v\u0103n b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1ef1c quan h\u01a1n v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh n\u00f3 tr\u00f4ng nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n.<\/p>\r\n<p><em>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u trong n\u0103m 2019<\/em><em style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\">.<\/em><em style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\">\u00a0 Hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh g\u1ee3i \u00fd hay ho cho b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 logo th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep.html\/\">d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-tieng-anh.html\/\">b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-website-tphcm.html\/\">website<\/a> &#8230; th\u00ec h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay v\u1edbi \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho n\u0103m 2019 chuy\u1ec3n sang hai con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 ho\u00e0i c\u1ed5, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c xu&#8230;<\/p>\n